      "content_license": "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body": "<p>I believe that the behaviour you want can't be done purely in Jolt on [jolt-demo](<a href=\"https://jolt-demo.appspot.com/#inception\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://jolt-demo.appspot.com/#inception</a>) because it doesn't support quoting elements inside <code>join</code> or <code>modify-overwrite-beta</code> the way you want. You need to do the quoting in code after Jolt transformation.</p>\n<p>The closest you'll get to your desired output (besides the result you already have) would be an array:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-json prettyprint-override\"><code>[\n  {\n    &quot;operation&quot;: &quot;shift&quot;,\n    &quot;spec&quot;: {\n      &quot;*&quot;: {\n        &quot;PIN&quot;: &quot;PINS[]&quot; \n      }\n    }\n  }\n]\n</code></pre>\n<pre class=\"lang-json prettyprint-override\"><code>{\n  &quot;PINS&quot;: [\n    &quot;43001005357&quot;,\n    &quot;59001024356&quot;\n  ]\n}\n</code></pre>\n",
